 of Form, 5., intern. Ausgabe. Leipzig: Bohmeier, 2008.</span><span class=\"newline\"></span><a href=\"https://scholar.google.com/scholar?q=Spencer-Brown%2C%20George%20%281969%29%3A%20Laws%20of%20Form%2C%205.%2C%20intern.%20Ausgabe.%20Leipzig%3A%20Bohmeier%2C%202008.\" class=\"link link-external googleScholar\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Suche in Google Scholar</a></p>\n\t\n\t<p class=\"reference\" id=\"j_sosys-2023-0001_ref_020\"><span class=\"reference-mixed-citation\">von Bertalanffy, Ludwig (1968): General System Theory: Foundations, Developments, Applications. New York: Braziller.</span><span class=\"newline\"></span><a href=\"https://scholar.google.com/scholar?q=von%20Bertalanffy%2C%20Ludwig%20%281968%29%3A%20General%20System%20Theory%3A%20Foundations%2C%20Developments%2C%20Applications.%20New%20York%3A%20Braziller.\" class=\"link link-external googleScholar\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Suche in Google Scholar</a></p>\n\t\n\t<p class=\"reference\" id=\"j_sosys-2023-0001_ref_021\"><span class=\"reference-mixed-citation\">von Foerster, Heinz (1993): Gegenstände: greifbare Symbole für (Eigen-)Verhalten, in: ders., Wissen und Gewissen: Versuch einer Brücke, hrsg. von Siegfried J. Schmidt. Frankfurt a.M.: Suhrkamp, 103–115.</span><span class=\"newline\"></span><a href=\"https://scholar.google.com/scholar?q=von%20Foerster%2C%20Heinz%20%281993%29%3A%20Gegenst%C3%A4nde%3A%20greifbare%20Symbole%20f%C3%BCr%20%28Eigen-%29Verhalten%2C%20in%3A%20ders.%2C%20Wissen%20und%20Gewissen%3A%20Versuch%20einer%20Br%C3%BCcke%2C%20hrsg.%20von%20Siegfried%20J.%20Schmidt.%20Frankfurt%20a.M.%3A%20Suhrkamp%2C%20103%E2%80%93115.\" class=\"link link-external googleScholar\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">Suche in Google Scholar</a></p>\n\t\n\t<p class=\"reference\" id=\"j_sosys-2023-0001_ref_022\"><span class=\"reference-mixed-citation\">White, Harrison C. (2008): Identity and Control: How Social Formations Emer